%*****************************************************************************************************************************************%
%*********************************************************** `my-packages.sty' ***********************************************************%
%*****************************************************************************************************************************************%
% Encapsulates all of the package requirements into a single package, including optional packages conditionally loaded based on the package options given to the 'my-latex' package.  Common LaTeX packages, potentially useful packages, and packages that were but are not currently being used are still loaded to ensure these packages do not clash with any of the packages currently in use or any of the macros/commands/environments defined during development.  The current assumption is that the LaTeX engine is used, but this package will eventually include conditional package loading and other dependencies to support other TeX engines (e.g. XeLaTeX/LuaLaTeX)
%*****************************************************************************************************************************************%
